      <title>斯里兰卡总统在新内阁中保留财政部长职位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/sri-lankan-president-keeps-finance-minister-s-job-in-new-cabinet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯里兰卡总统阿努拉·库马拉·迪萨纳亚克在上周举行的议会选举中赢得了历史性的绝对多数，并于周一为 21 名内阁部长主持了宣誓就职仪式，同时保留了财政部和国防部长职务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/sri-lankan-president-keeps-finance-minister-s-job-in-new-cabinet</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 12:59:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
